## Drawing

Add a timer
  #time/timer += [period: 1]

The value to print
  #value = #time/timer.ticks{1}

Set up drawing elements 
  #text = [
    shape: "text" 
    parameters: [
      x: 120
      y: 150
      text: #value
      font: [size: 60 face: "Calibri"]
    ]
  ]

Draw a Pacman
  canvas = [
    type: "canvas" 
    contains: [|shape parameters| #text] 
    parameters: [width: 500 height: 500]
  ]
  #html/app = [
    root: "mech-root" 
    contains: [|type contains parameters| canvas]
  ]